<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM2.2.7">
<l>tiṅka ḷappu vāṉerikā lākiti caimukaṉār</l>
<l>taṅka ḷappaṉ cāmiyappaṉ pākat tiruntavaṇṭuṇ</l>
<l>toṅka lappu nīṇmuṭiyāṉ cūḻkaḻal cūṭaniṉṟa</l>
<l>veṅka ḷappa ṉemperumā ṉevvuḷ kiṭantāṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Becoming the moon, water, the heavens, fire, and wind,</l>
<l>Father of him facing the directions, lord father, our father who stands</l>
<l>So that his round anklets crown the one who is [his] half</l>
<l rend="indent">with a high hair knot,</l>
<l>Water, and a garland where bees sup, our great lord,</l>
<l rend="indent">he is the one who lies in Evvuḷ.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
